<h2>lifx: Control 'LIFX' Smart Light Bulbs</h2>
<p>Allows you to read and change the state of 'LIFX' smart light bulbs via the 'LIFX' developer api &lt;<a href="https://api.developer.lifx.com/">https://api.developer.lifx.com/</a>&gt;.
    Covers most 'LIFX' api endpoints, including changing light color and brightness, selecting lights by id, group or location as well as activating effects.</p>
